name: The Twin-Bound Camellians
description: Hailing from the Amethyst Mines, the The Twin-Bound Camellians are known for their skill in shadow magic. Specifically moving from shadow and shadow, smuggling goods within the shadows of clueless civilians. Now finally free from the prison cells of the Gibbun, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
